title: Cold Therapy - Embrace the Silence - dark electro industrial ebm
description:
Artist: Cold Therapy
Album: Embrace the Silence
Genre: dark electro, aggrotech, ebm, industrial, goth, gothic, electronic
Label: Halotan Records
Year: 2013

Embrace the silence is modern and very well produced piece of dancefloor oriented dark electronic music. The production is immaculate and synth lines are catchy what makes the whole release a must-have for any follower of dark electronic sounds.

More information: www.halotan.net
